OL,7,FBut ultimately what really matters are
OL,8,Fthe stories, how they are produced and
OL,9,Fthe programme running orders. The     
OL,10,Fconcern over the future of the BBC News
OL,11,FChannel serves as a reminder of this. 
OL,13,FThe BBC's international news coverage 
OL,14,Fis one of its greatest strengths.     
OL,16,FForeign news is about more than the   
OL,17,Fcoverage of a major story like the war
OL,18,Fin Ukraine. It is about trying to     
OL,19,Fproduce a good range of stories from  
OL,20,Facross the globe which are of interest
OL,21,For importance to viewers.             
